## E-commerce Integration

This template includes a mock Shopify Buy Button. For production use, see the three integration paths:

1. **Buy Button (Simplest)** — Replace the mock handler with the [Shopify Buy Button JS SDK](https://shopify.github.io/js-buy-sdk/)
2. **Headless Commerce** — Fetch products from Shopify Storefront API, use the built-in cart
3. **Custom Backend** — Connect to your own database + Stripe for full control

The cart system uses a shared module-level store (`cart-store.js`) that works across all sections without React context.

